m\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26120,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/03\/26\/door-masajid-women\/","url_meta":{"origin":23051,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Mosques: The Prophet makes women&#8217;s door in Masjid","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 26, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIt would be better if you had left this door to the mosque for women.\u201d Nafi\u2019 said, \u201cIbn Umar never again entered through it until the day he died.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 462 Grade: Sahih\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":23979,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/11\/02\/treat-women-best-way\/","url_meta":{"origin":23051,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Women: Best men treat women in best manner","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 2, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe best of you are the best to their women.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 1978 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0645\u0652\u0631\u064d\u0648 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u06